[Avian influenza continues to march across North America with a wake of dead birds and devastated individuals.

Biosecurity cannot be overemphasized, whether you are a commercial production facility or a school student preparing to show a bird. But sadly, the shows are cancelled in effort to protect the birds. Biosecurity is everyone's priority when it comes to the birds. Guard your birds, inside, and limit the number of individuals coming onto your premises. - Mod.TG

